    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solo</h2>Fart around collecting keys and coins to purchase skins.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229230/extras/f18a2be930e0d15cd8f171d181069bcd.poster.avif?t=1723711806\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229230/extras/f18a2be930e0d15cd8f171d181069bcd.webm?t=1723711806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229230/extras/f18a2be930e0d15cd8f171d181069bcd.mp4?t=1723711806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play With Friends!</h2>Play <strong>with</strong> or <strong>against</strong> your friends (soon-to-be foes) to see who the crassest of them all is!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229230/extras/a871cfbfbf232654227c10c57b6a9f8b.poster.avif?t=1723711806\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229230/extras/a871cfbfbf232654227c10c57b6a9f8b.webm?t=1723711806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229230/extras/a871cfbfbf232654227c10c57b6a9f8b.mp4?t=1723711806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Premise</h2><br>In a world where twerking is the only way to be respected in society, HotBunz is a game about how a new sport, the Bootylympics, allows the citizens of Buttopia to rise above the ranks by being as crass and show-boaty as they can.<br><br>The rules of the <strong>Bootylympics</strong> are as quirky as the Buttopians themselves. Participants must navigate through a series of challenges that showcase their ability to shimmy, shake, and twirl with unmatched finesse. From synchronized booty bouncing to gravity-defying farting, every move is meticulously judged by a panel of esteemed cheek connoisseurs.<br><br>Play as your favorite Buttopian in this physics-based 2D Platformer Party Game with your friends and claim all the glory. Always remember, Champion Buttopians always come dressed to kill.<br><br><br>- Play Solo to collect as many coins and buy character skins<br>- Play against friends in different game modes to really show them who's who<br>- Fart Fire (Pretty cool, we know)<br>- Dress your Buttopian up to show up and show off!<br>- Most Importantly, <strong>HAVE FUN!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls XBOX</h2><br>A - Fart<br>B - SuperFart<br>RT - Grapple<br>LT - Steal Key From Player<br>L Analog - Movement<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyboard</h2><br>WASD - Movement <br>R Shift - Grapple  <br>Space Bar - Fart<br>Next level -  Space Bar",
